  "detailed_description": "<strong><u>Sinister Hospital : Judge Harlan Story</u></strong><br><br>In the dark forests of Duskwood town, an abandoned hospital rises like a ghost. Although \"Sinister Hospital\" had been closed for years, it still harbors dreadful secrets within. The player steps into the hospital to trace the footsteps of a group of lost children from the town's outskirts. However, inside awaits only a dark adventure and a quest for forgotten justice: Judge Harlan.<br><br>Chapter 1: Entrance<br><br>The game opens with the player navigating through the gloomy forests of Duskwood. Amidst old ruins and forgotten paths, the silhouette of the abandoned hospital catches the player's eye. Initial puzzles greet the player in this forest, such as gathering pieces of an old map to find the right path or deciphering ancient symbols to unlock hidden passages.<br><br>Chapter 2: Dollhouse of Horrors<br><br>Upon entering the hospital, the player finds themselves in a room resembling a dollhouse. It's filled with old and eerie-looking dolls. Some dolls provide clues to progress or are necessary to solve puzzles. However, some come to life and stalk the player through dark corridors.<br><br>Chapter 3: Traces of Judge Harlan<br><br>As the player delves deeper into the hospital, they begin to uncover traces of Judge Harlan. His story comes to life through horrifying diaries written on the walls and old records. However, during this quest, the player encounters more complex puzzles and dangerous traps. For example, hacking the hospital's old security system to open a passage or finding hidden keys in forgotten rooms.<br><br>Chapter 4: Dreadful Truth<br><br>As the player approaches unraveling Judge Harlan's secret and the hospital's dark past, puzzles become more challenging, and the dolls become more menacing. While delving into the mysterious world of dolls to uncover the truth, the player also encounters dark forces. For instance, getting lost in a maze guided by dolls or engaging in a challenging fight to defeat the puppet master.<br><br>Features:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/dd479ae2d5ba066d444aeda8897139a6.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/dd479ae2d5ba066d444aeda8897139a6.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/dd479ae2d5ba066d444aeda8897139a6.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can examine or pick up items around you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/3fd37be984feced6f849b068cfbd124e.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/3fd37be984feced6f849b068cfbd124e.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/3fd37be984feced6f849b068cfbd124e.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can examine it as a detective.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/29a9b1f4fea05582f179e64364d19fac.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/29a9b1f4fea05582f179e64364d19fac.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/29a9b1f4fea05582f179e64364d19fac.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dolls Will Do Their Best to Scare You.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/c80b0c6f189e4ac140f39b589d2a2ade.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/c80b0c6f189e4ac140f39b589d2a2ade.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/c80b0c6f189e4ac140f39b589d2a2ade.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>This hospital is not what you think, I think it is possessed by spirits<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/859c063589fc37a2cca1ed84006e5eb4.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/859c063589fc37a2cca1ed84006e5eb4.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/859c063589fc37a2cca1ed84006e5eb4.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>We need to find the mysterious codes to open the chest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/cfe363606ac03cb635c2959f2d13e97d.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/cfe363606ac03cb635c2959f2d13e97d.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/cfe363606ac03cb635c2959f2d13e97d.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You have to deal with the puzzle and solve it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/d4af27cf47efb6c09310f49f29331026.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/d4af27cf47efb6c09310f49f29331026.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/d4af27cf47efb6c09310f49f29331026.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Sinister Butler will never leave you alone. As if the other dolls weren't enough, this one will haunt you too.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/e34a0846d50a8048cbb03342a10f0cb0.poster.avif?t=1745414438\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/e34a0846d50a8048cbb03342a10f0cb0.webm?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916310/extras/e34a0846d50a8048cbb03342a10f0cb0.mp4?t=1745414438\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Light sources are not unlimited, you must find the batteries hidden in the hospital.",
